&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.patreon.com/AnduoGames&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Patreon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://store.steampowered.com/app/3400350/Third_Crisis_Neon_Nights/?curator_clanid=36621521&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
